# Repository Preflight Check

Before implementing any new feature:

1. Scan the repository.
2. Identify existing documentation, architecture files, and design rules.
3. Verify whether all required files exist.

Required files:

/design/ui-design-rules.md
/design/screen-registry.md
/docs/architecture.md
/docs/api.md
/docs/app-flow.md

If required files are missing:
- Report them
- Ask the user whether to generate them

Do not begin implementation until the repository audit is complete.